All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, AbsQueryChild
public class ConsQGVertex
extends QGVertex

A special type of QGVertex that has been consolidated, i.e. brought into SQL memory. NB: Unlike other QGItems, ConsQGVertex's contents are *not* meaningful: name, condEle, and annotEle.
